\" last month. The reaction was also inspired by Abe's visit to in December.\nUnder Japan's pacifist constitution, the country has not been able to engage in militaristic combat since the end of World War II.\nCommenters related the move to escalated tensions with China, who had set up an over a part of the , including Japan's , in November last year. "}
