ts run on the basis of Constitution. I believe a government has one religion and that's India First\".\nThe outgoing Prime Minister released a statement: \"As I have said on many occasions, my life and tenure in public office are an open book. I have always tried to do my best in serving this great nation of ours. In the last ten years, we as a country have seen many successes and achievements that we should be proud of. Today, India is a far stronger country in every respect than it was a decade ago.\""}
